text: Calbha Beag is an uninhabited island in Eddrachillis Bay, off Sutherland, Highland, Scotland. It is immediately to the west of Calbha Mor. thumb An estimate of the area from Ordnance Survey suggest a figure of about , although it has been listed by Rick Livingstone as totalling , possibly including areas exposed at low tide. ==Notes== ==References== * Category:Islands of Sutherland Category:Uninhabited islands of Highland (council area)
